title: "CrystalCanvas"
abstract: "A next-generation, open-source desktop application for crystal structure modeling, GPU-accelerated volumetric visualization, Brillouin Zone and Wannier tight-binding analysis, and DFT/MD file preparation. Built on Rust, wgpu, and C++."
